{"tid":2300932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（割席了） 蓬佩奧：國務院已開始權力移交工作 ！","createTime":"2020-11-26T02:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T05:21:06.000Z","uid":118346,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b430941a897e06712a245fd353527834b4f59ea9","tid":2300932,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:29:12.000Z","msg":"Pompeo says U.S. State Department transition process begun<br />\n<br />\n(Reuters) - U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo on Tuesday indicated that the State Department has begun the transition process after the General Services Administration (GSA), the federal agency that must sign off on presidential transitions, on Monday told President-elect Joe Biden he could formally begin the hand-over.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Today we began the process to see what the GSA's decision was, and will do everything that's required by law. We'll make this work,&quot; Pompeo said in an interview with Fox News."},{"pid":"ce1fbaef410e6cc402d75561d24ed7a869939f84","tid":2300932,"uid":61091,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:30:26.000Z","msg":"Deep state<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cf9488ccd9e4a2ef0db5eb26fba69223fbfb2f","tid":2300932,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d56a8232d4ab5353a3608ce4c3ac1b1db323a5","tid":2300932,"uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"The Department has received notice that pursuant to the Presidential Transition Act, the GSA Administrator is making certain post-election resources and services available to the Biden-Harris Transition Team. This evening, DOD has been contacted by the Biden-Harris team and their designated lead for the DOD Agency Review Team and, based on the ascertainment by the GSA Administrator, <span class=\"red\">we will begin immediately implementing our plan to provide support in accordance with statute, DOD policy and the memorandum of agreement between the White House and the Biden-Harris team.  The DOD Transition Task Force will arrange and coordinate all DOD contact with the Biden-Harris team.  DOD is prepared to provide post-election services and support in a professional, orderly, and efficient manner that is befitting of the public&rsquo;s expectation of the Department and our commitment to national security.</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國防部都話會立即配合拜登交接工作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cae1263712a4070cf1b1e2464bb81c0b999d5d","tid":2300932,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6d56a8232d4ab5353a3608ce4c3ac1b1db323a5","tid":2300932,"uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:35:34.000Z","msg":"The Department has received notice that pursuant to the Presidential Transition Act, the GSA Administrator is making certain post-election resources and services available to the Biden-Harris Transition Team. This evening, DOD has been contacted by the Biden-Harris team and their designated lead for the DOD Agency Review Team and, based on the ascertainment by the GSA Administrator, <span class=\"red\">we will begin immediately implementing our plan to provide support in accordance with statute, DOD policy and the memorandum of agreement between the White House and the Biden-Harris team.  The DOD Transition Task Force will arrange and coordinate all DOD contact with the Biden-Harris team.  DOD is prepared to provide post-election services and support in a professional, orderly, and efficient manner that is befitting of the public&rsquo;s expectation of the Department and our commitment to national security.</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國防部都話會立即配合拜登交接工作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"點解要遺棄侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e78de72f0a6b587605b654845f9a10887e19c4d","tid":2300932,"uid":236171,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"收皮啦又帶風向<br />\n侵自己叫佢做架<br />\n<br />\n都有講明批准 Transition 唔代表認輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1331013908971261953?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1331013908971261953%3Fs%3D19&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=b94d4af4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1331013908971261953%3Fs%3D19&h=68bc0b90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1331013908971261953?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1331247567041081345?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1331247567041081345%3Fs%3D19&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=000f5947\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1331247567041081345%3Fs%3D19&h=494e0b90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/